Package: ConfigINI
Type: Package
Title: A Fast INI File Parser
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
  person("Dyfan", "Jones", email="dyfan.r.jones@gmail.com", role= c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides a simple yet efficient parser for INI configuration files,
  converting them into structured list formats for easy manipulation and access
  within R. The structured list can seamlessly be written back to an INI
  configuration file, ensuring smooth round-trip data handling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
